title: Natl Newsletter
author: gavbea
pages:
#- xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx§0
§0                            Hello everyone,§0
§0
§0I am gavbea and I have been recently made Minister of Land Management and National Pride under recently seated Chancellor xlxENVYZxlx. I will be overseeing the use of land making sure 
#- that the space with have within our borders is optimally used. That includes the farm district and the residential district. As for my part on national pride I am charged with the responsibility of promoting Alpoko inside and out of the country. I plan 
#- to have events that will be fun for all and make people like you play more :)§0
§0
§0I came up with this idea, to make a newsletter of some sorts to speak directly to every person in Alpoko. You should expect new ones of these from time to time again
#- It's my hope that many people will read these and give feedback or responses to me I'd love to hear what you guys want to say §0
§0
§0Sugguestions or questions to me on the newsletter or to the other cabinet members on their roles would be greatly appreciated. 
#- With a new Chancellor came a new constitution as well. Our 2nd constitution sets up a legislative branch of our gov't. Anybody can propose a law! :D §0
§0
§0The Royal Court is also established. One of our hardest workers ActionJackson has been appointed as the
#- Royal Judge.§0
§0
§0Territories and colonies are the subject of article VII of the constitution, (look forward to expansion!)§0
§0
§0A link to a google doc for the whole constitution can be found pinned in #alpokogeneral.
#- Chancellor Envyz has posted new building codes in a post on /r/Alpoko. The building codes layout the permitted areas for buildings under 3 and over 4 stories high, and the theme residents must attempt to build in. All buildings are to be made in the 
#- Edwardian theme as shown in Chancellor Envyz' post. §0
§0
§0Help and supplies can be given if asked, I myself will be glad to help anyone with any build or project :)§0
§0

#- As part of my role as Minister of National Pride, I would like to annouce the launch of a contest for the banner of our nation! Submissions should be made to me on discord using §0needcoolshoes.com/banner§0 OR be thrown into my hopper mailbox located at
#- my home next to the bridge. §0
§0
§0
§0If you are feeling insecure because you have no ender pearls, I can give you some! Just ask me and I will put one in your mailbox if you are away, or I can give you one in person.
#- Thank you for reading this issue of my newsletter to you. Once again I, gavbea, will be writing these every so often to keep citizens informed and feeling sure you are spoken to and heard from. I look forward to your feedback and sugguestions!
#- 
§0
§0===-=-=-=-=-=-=-=== -------------------   Long live the King!§0
§0   Long live Alpoko!§0
§0-------------------===-=-=-=-=-=-=-===§0
§0
